 stir in with spatula. Place steamed clams in a serving dish. Pour over rice and stir a little with spatula. Garnish with remaining 1 Tbsp parsley and serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If paella rice is not available, substitute with another short grain rice such as risotto rice."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","1h 15m","6 portions"]}